        <span class="score" id="score_16525087">122 points</span> by <a href="user?id=rbanffy" class="hnuser">rbanffy</a> <span class="age"><a href="item?id=16525087">12 hours ago</a></span> <span id="unv_16525087"></span> | <a href="hide?id=16525087&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D16525087">hide</a> | <a href="https://hn.algolia.com/?query=The%20Great%20Lightbulb%20Conspiracy&sort=byDate&dateRange=all&type=story&storyText=false&prefix&page=0" class="hnpast">past</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=The%20Great%20Lightbulb%20Conspiracy">web</a> | <a href="fave?id=16525087&amp;auth=cd03e262cac5d6ea39bb23c0dd43284564ffe718">favorite</a> | <a href="item?id=16525087">70&nbsp;comments</a>              </td></tr>
