                  <span class="c00">I would be interested in an economy that incentivized repair rather than replacement.  Maybe make repairs tax-free or even a tax credit.<span>
              </span><div class='reply'>        <p><font size="1">
                      <u><a href="reply?id=16526877&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D16525087%2316526877">reply</a></u>
